Title: Liv
Writer: Pål Løkkeberg, Vibeke Løkkeberg, Sverre Udnæs
Actors: Vibeke Løkkeberg, Per Theodor Haugen, Bente Børsum, Helen Brinchmann
Plot: A day in the life of photo model Liv. But it's no ordinary day. She's break up with her fiance, father and her own empty life as a model, and has to find a new place to live. But is it that easy to make a clean break?
